title: SBI Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 122 Manager Posts
description: The State Bank of India (SBI) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 122 Manager and Deputy Manager Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their B.E./B. Tech in Computer Science, Electrical, Electronics Engineering, MCA, MBA, Any Degree,  Post-graduation, can apply for the SBI Recruitment 2025 . The interested applicants can apply in online mode.
